name: ThumbnailResponse
summary: Simple object passed to the thumbnail callback in response to the requestThumbnailImagesAtTimes method.

properties.name: code
properties.description: Error code will be 0 if success is true, nonzero otherwise. If the error was generated by the operating system, that system's error value is used. Otherwise, this value will be -1.

properties.name: time
properties.summary: Time offset for the thumbnail, in seconds.
